index=19>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Trio of Terror....</span><hr size=1> In a blaze of red flames and wild mist, Alecto appeared. She shook her head wildly as she came to a stop. She smoothed a hand over her wild blonde hair and looked to the Olympians. &quot;A party I see.&quot; She smiled glancing around. &quot;Without Moi?&quot; She held her petite little hand to herself and laughed slightly.<br>
<br>
In a  blaze of blue flames and wild mist, Megaera appeared. She grinned as she crossed her legs sitting on the top of an empty chair perching herself against the rim of it. She ran a hand through her long brown hair and laughed a bit. &quot;But a party is not a party without a Furie.&quot;<br>
<br>
In a blaze of black flames and wild mist, Tisiphone appeared. She unlike her sisters, sat in the corner looking at the aray of Gods on Olympus.<br>
<br>
Alecto smiled as she pushed the red strings on her outfit behind her as she walked over to Apollo dragging her hand lightly across his shoulders as she moved to the other side of the Sun God. &quot;Welcome back Apollo.&quot; She smiled and crossed to the rest of the Gods.<br>
<br>
Megaera hopped down from the chair and moved her way towards Apollo as well merely waving at him with a snicker and a grin. <br>
<br>
They both then walked over towards Hera and bowed politely. &quot;Dear Hera. It is good to see that you are well.&quot; They said in unision. Megaera then looked towards Zeus as she snagged a chalice from one of the others and held it high. &quot;To Apollo's return.&quot; She then downed the liquid smiling.<br>
<br>
